title: Club Babylon, Ahmedabad
address: Babylon club road, SP road, Nr. Science city circle, Bahadaj, Ahmedabad - 380060
shortDescription: RECLAIM LEISURE, RECLAIM LIFE. EVERYTHING ELSE CAN WAIT.
longDescription: Towering tall above the ground, and nestling well below it too; Club Babylon flaunts an architecture that you have hardly seen before.
footerDescription: Gorgeously spread over 47,000 square yards, Club Babylon has a predominant sense of vastness and opulence. Neighbour to an enchanting lake garden - a magnificent 80,000 square yards of flora and fauna, nature is in full bloom in and around Club Babylon.
